create table if not exists TMP.TMP_KCB_CUST_LIST_T0_TMP_201908121300_606 stored as ORCFile as select A.cust_code
,c.cust_name
,case when a.kcb_open_date is not null and (B.rating_lvl<=3 or t0.rating_lvl<=3) and nvl(agmt.has_sign_2F,0)=0 then 1 else 0 end need_c3
,case when a.kcb_open_date is not null and (age>=70) and nvl(agmt.has_sign_2D,0)=0 then 1 else 0  end need_age
,case when fisl_c.credit_cuacct_code is not null and fisl_inst.fisl_status=0 and nvl(agmt.has_sign_2E,0)=0 
 AND fisl_c.credit_open_date<20190722  then 1 else 0  end need_fisl
,c.inst_org
,c.inst_brch_name
,c.crm_inst_org_id
,c.crm_brch_name
,sj.telephone
,zh.main_cuacct_code
,A.kcb_open_date 
,kt.open_date kcb_sq_date
,B.rating_lvl rating_lvl_SIGN,b.rating_exp_date rating_exp_date_SIGN
,c.rating_lvl,c.rating_exp_date,c.rating_date 
,if(e.cust_code is not null,1,0) is_xgsg   ,if(d.cust_code is not null,1,0) is_cgzq   ,if(fisl.cust_code is not null,1,0) is_fisl_xgzq   ,if(fislkc.cust_code is not null,1,0) is_fisl_kczq   ,t0.rating_lvl rating_lvl_t0,t0.rating_exp_date rating_exp_date_t0,t0.rating_date rating_date_t0,age
,fisl_c.credit_cuacct_code
,fisl_c.credit_open_date
,fisl_inst.fisl_inst_org_id_combine
,fisl_inst.fisl_inst_brch_name
,aum.aum_20t_tavg
from FACT.UI_INDEX_MODULE_CUST_KCB_INFO A  
LEFT JOIN (
	SELECT usercode CUST_CODE,substr(max(open_date),1,8) open_date
		FROM MID.MID_A_SISDATA_KCB_INFO T
	WHERE dt=20190811 AND open_status='1'
	group by usercode
) kt on kt.CUST_CODE=a.CUST_CODE LEFT JOIN (
	SELECT dt,CUST_CODE,rating_lvl,rating_exp_date
	FROM BASE.UDS_B_A_CUST_INFO
	where dt>=20190309
) b on b.cust_code=a.cust_code and b.dt=kt.open_date     LEFT JOIN (
	SELECT dt,CUST_CODE,rating_lvl,rating_exp_date,rating_date
	,inst_org,b.brch_name inst_brch_name,crm_inst_org_id,c.brch_name crm_brch_name,cust_name
	FROM (select * from FACT.UI_INDEX_MODULE_CUST_BASIC_INFO where dt=20190811 ) a 
	left join dim.DM_BRANCH_NEW_2017 b on a.inst_org=b.jz_cd 
	left join dim.DM_BRANCH_NEW_2017 c on a.crm_inst_org_id=c.jz_cd 
	
	
) c on c.cust_code=a.cust_code 

LEFT JOIN (
	SELECT CUST_CODE,rating_lvl,rating_exp_date,rating_date
	FROM BASE.UDS_B_A_CUST_INFO_T1
	where dt=20190811 
) t0 on t0.cust_code=a.cust_code 

left join (
	select cust_code,telephone
	from FACT.UI_INDEX_MODULE_CUST_COMBINE
	where dt=20190811
) sj on sj.cust_code=a.cust_code 

left join (
	select cust_code,main_cuacct_code
	from FACT.UI_INDEX_MODULE_ACCOUT
	where dt=20190811
) zh on zh.cust_code=a.cust_code 


left join (
	select distinct t.cust_code from (
	SELECT A.cust_code 
	FROM mid.MID_KGDB_IPO_HANDOVER A  
	where dt>=20190627  and secu_intl like '1787%'
	union all
	SELECT A.cust_code 
	FROM mid.MID_I_FISL_KGDB_IPO_HANDOVER A  
	where dt>=20190627 and secu_intl like '1787%' 
	) t
) d on d.cust_code=a.cust_code

left join (
	select distinct cust_code
	from base.UDS_B_I_TRADE_MOVT
	where dt>=20190627 and TRD_TYPE='h'  ) e on e.cust_code=a.cust_code

left join (
select cust_code,aum_ex['aum_20t_tavg'] aum_20t_tavg
from FACT.UI_INDEX_MODULE_ASSET_ALL
where dt=20190809
) aum on aum.cust_code=a.cust_code

left join (
select cust_code
   ,case when  cust_code in (
 181133503,192124133,182611612,196446785,180825786,181147190,181138158,191249459,182070119,180767561) then 70 else age end as age
	from FACT.UDS_F_A_FISL_SUITABLE_CUST
	where dt=20190811
) ag on ag.cust_code=a.cust_code 
left join (
select cust_code,credit_cuacct_code,credit_open_date
	from FACT.UI_INDEX_MODULE_ACCOUT 
	where dt=20190811 and credit_cuacct_code is not null
) fisl_c on fisl_c.cust_code=a.cust_code 
left join (
select cust_code,fisl_inst_org_id_combine,b.brch_name fisl_inst_brch_name,fisl_status
	from (select cust_code,fisl_inst_org_id_combine,fisl_status from FACT.UI_INDEX_MODULE_FISL_OPEN where dt=20190811)  a
	left join dim.DM_BRANCH_NEW_2017 b on a.fisl_inst_org_id_combine=b.jz_cd 
) fisl_inst on fisl_inst.cust_code=a.cust_code 
left join (
	select distinct CUST_CODE
	from MID.MID_A_FISL_AGENT_AGREEMENT M
    where M.DT=20190811 AND M.AGENT_BIZ_TYPE='*'
) fislkc on fislkc.CUST_CODE=a.CUST_CODE
left join (
	SELECT distinct cust_code 
	FROM mid.MID_I_FISL_KGDB_IPO_HANDOVER A  
	where dt>=20190627 and secu_intl like '1787%' 
) fisl on fisl.cust_code=a.cust_code
left join (
select cust_code
       ,max(case when cust_agmt_type='2D' then 1 else 0 end) as has_sign_2D
       ,max(case when cust_agmt_type='2E' then 1 else 0 end) as has_sign_2E
       ,max(case when cust_agmt_type='2F' then 1 else 0 end) as has_sign_2F
from tmp.A_KBSSUSER_CUST_AGREEMENT_T0 t 
where cust_agmt_type in('2D','2E','2F') and dt='201908121300'
group by cust_code
) agmt on agmt.cust_code=a.cust_code

where a.dt=20190811 
and (a.kcb_open_date is not null or (fisl_c.credit_cuacct_code is not null  and fisl_inst.fisl_status=0))
